{
  "stem": "1338.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And today, teaching myself, I-- I agree that maybe you cannot teach anybody anything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You can make them only-- we can only show them how to learn.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "However, I have to say that when you are a child and you are impressioned, then of course, good teachers can make the difference.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was a B student.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- my-- my talents and my inclinations have changed with time, very strangely so, because when I was a child, age of 10, 12, I had difficulty with languages in general.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I wasn't very good at languages.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was exposed to languages, because my father, besides his lumber yard business, somehow or other got involved in publishing about before World War I and during it.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so-- so we had a house full of books.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my mother, whose Polish was much better than my father's-- my father never really learned Polish that well.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My mother did very well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And by the way, they-- they did not speak to me any other language but Polish, because it was very important to retain the purity of pronunciation.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So that-- but anyway, my mother still read me stories from Russian storybooks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I have, obviously, learned at least how to read it and how to understand it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't speak it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But anyway-- [SIGHS] so-- so I had difficulty in languages.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And from-- and I very good at math.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I-- I had a child prodigy type of counting, because my mother would teach me how to count when I was two years old to make me eat or whatever she wanted to do.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my most-- the greatest entertainment, the thing I liked most is to count.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And so it became obvious that I will become an engineer.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
